platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Open this Apple Design Award winner and start coloring. In moments, all your stresses just kinda wash away, right? That’s the nice side effect of this tremendous coloring app. It’s packed with creativity-enhancing tools—spray paint, customized color palettes, and a huge assortment of intuitive features. Our favorite pictures switch from coloring between the lines to going rogue.
這款曾獲 Apple Design Awards 設計獎的填色 App 滿載能提昇創意的工具，包括噴漆、自訂調色板等，讓你畫出天馬行空的作品。
Open this Apple Design Award winner and start colouring. It’s packed with creativity enhancing tools – spray paint, customised palettes and more – that will encourage you to colour outside the lines.
Apple Design Awardを受賞したアプリを開いて、塗り絵を始めましょう。スプレー塗料やカスタマイズされたパレットなど、創造性を高めてくれるツールが豊富にそろっているので、型にはまらない塗り絵を楽しめます。

Open this Apple Design Award winner and start colouring. In moments, all your stresses just kinda wash away, right? That’s the nice side effect of this tremendous colouring app. It’s packed with creativity-enhancing tools—spray paint, customized colour palettes, and a huge assortment of intuitive features. Our favourite pictures switch from colouring between the lines to going rogue.
在這款榮獲 Apple 設計大獎的作品裡，你可以運用噴筆、客製化調色盤等各種工具發揮創意，激發你突破界限的想像力。

Lancez cette app lauréate d’un Apple Design Award et commencez à colorier. Elle propose de multiples outils d’amélioration de la créativité (des bombes de peinture, des palettes personnalisées et plus) qui vous encouragent à dépasser les limites.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Relax with colouring and immerse yourself in beautiful art.
ユニークなイラストとリアルなツールでゆったりと塗り絵に没頭しませんか。
Essayez le dessin pour vous relaxer.
